monkeyi.lzh    429056  Approx time: 0:55 at 2400 baud, 1:51 at 1200 baud
Contributed by: jmcates  Date: Mon May 13 18:47:31 1991
This is the official demo of the latest game from LucasFilm
"The Secret of Monkey Island". The demo installs on a HD and
multitasks well, though it eats much RAM! I've made two install
scripts, one for floppy the other for HD. Read the install_notes
first. VERY nifty game! Awfully funny...;)
